thread.title: Tariffs won't hurt Boeing, but retaliation will

title: Tariffs won't hurt Boeing, but retaliation will
text:
Tariffs won't hurt Boeing, but retaliation will Wednesday, March 07, 2018 - 01:13 
President Donald Trump's plan to slap tariffs on imported steel and aluminum will barely budge the price of Boeing planes, but retaliation from countries, like China, could hurt the planemaker. Aleksandra Michalska reports.
